{"tid":1829543,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"耀才咁多門市, 有無人識整連豬貼紙幫佢裝飾下","createTime":"2020-01-18T22:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T10:08:17.000Z","uid":325838,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfc88df8405c8b98dd2c1e9b3f47330fb5d60e0","tid":1829543,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:14:04.000Z","msg":"大家千其千其唔好咁做<br />\n<br />\n平日9點至10點落盤繁忙時間打去問長問短, 阻住d 唔識用電腦同手機落盤既大客打電話落盤<br />\n<br />\n星期六日同夜晚時間人手唔夠, 打電話去問長問短搞到班輪更職員做到無癮無人返shift<br />\n<br />\n佢答得唔好千其唔好屌佢地老母個臭閪<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好因為佢地態度惡劣就問佢地職員編號, 打去投訴熱線投訴, 佢地搵萬零蚊咋<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好因為佢地答錯野去証監會投訴, 搞到公司比証監會罰錢<br />\n<br />\n千其千其唔好搞到佢地做唔到生意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWjHL1D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWjHL1D.jpg&h=dd7467c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c03d4e4e0a393f61fe5d375dfc0cc5cab67d4ce","tid":1829543,"uid":325838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:23:58.000Z","msg":"耀才必須炒的員工:<br />\n1. 吳越峰 (Frank Ng)<br />\n2. 蔡源浩 (Michael Choy)<br />\n3. 林達源 (Tim Lam)<br />\n4. 林鴻誼 (Jack Lam)<br />\n5. 黃嘉銘 (Ming Wong)<br />\n<br />\n5大炒魷, 缺一不可<br />\n唔炒的話我條氣唔順, 就會keep住跟進耀才背叛香港市民的事件"},{"pid":"bf746ee01a8075f2bad02c60040aa87840b885e1","tid":1829543,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:25:49.000Z","msg":"耀才葉茂林 Your have failed this city!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OqjOAm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OqjOAm.gif&h=f4c94785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n耀才葉茂林 Your have failed this city!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTa7XtL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTa7XtL.gif&h=2cea6dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n耀才葉茂林 Your have failed this city!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYSNXtP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYSNXtP.gif&h=5de2fc78&s={SIZE}\" 